data.description: This is the home you have been waiting for in the amenity-filled Brookside community! This home is truly a rarity in the community as it is tucked away at the end of a private pipestem, sitting on a quiet cul-de-sac, and on a pristine 0.66 of an acre. This meticulously kept home features 6 bedrooms, 4 full bathrooms, a large and updated gourmet kitchen which opens to a cozy family room, a stone accented fireplace, gleaming hardwood floors throughout the main level,  a large walk-out basement, and so much more! The multi-level deck is an entertainer's dream as it is perfect for hosting gatherings, grilling-out during a wonderful evening,  and watching the "big game" on the outdoor TV! The home shows better than new construction, you really have to see it for yourself. You will enjoy the over 7 miles of park-like walking trails encompassing the community. Two community pools, basketball courts, tennis courts, two playgrounds, and a fitness center in the main clubhouse. You will also find multiple fishing ponds in the neighborhood stocked by the HOA. Immerse yourself in the growing local businesses; Old Bust Head Brewery, The Farm Station Cafe, Vint Hill Winery, Vint Hill Coffee, Vint Hill Crossfit, Vint Hill Yoga, and the Covert Cafe just to name a few (all short distance from the house). You will also be 7 minutes from the Wegman's in Gainesville, 15 minutes from the Gainesville Promenade and Virginia Gateway shopping centers, and 10 minutes from Downtown Warrenton.  Commuters will also have easy  access to routes 28 and 29 as Brookside is conveniently located in the "DC side of Warrenton." This one is a must see!
